title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre willing to devote all your energy toward a task once youre convinced your participation is essential. However, overcoming your uncertainty could be the most challenging part today. You need to be coaxed, not from doubt or disbelief, but because youre probably already juggling too many obligations. You want to know that your efforts wont be wasted if you put aside some of your current activities to focus elsewhere. But be careful of diving in with too much zest. You can easily exhaust yourself if you try to do too much at once. Pace yourself, and your enthusiasm will help you deliver more than you promise. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
